{"tid":508573,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"你 Pay 我都 Pay LG 手機支付系統 LG Pay 2018 年登場","createTime":"2017-12-24T11:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T11:21:12.000Z","uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2c0f3592527256c7e776b75e48d784ca2fecb83f","tid":508573,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/optimize.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2Foptimize.jpg&h=f72235e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近年不少科技公司都形形式式的手機支付，你又在用一款呢 ? 南韓電子消費品牌 LG 宣佈會在 2018年開始推動自家的手機支付服務 LG Pay。和 Samsung Pay 不同的是，LG Pay 是採用無線磁通訊技術 (WMC)，用戶只需將 LG 手機與刷卡機接觸，並透過指紋認證就是可以完成交易。<br />\n<br />\n其實，LG 在2016年7月已經發表了 LG Pay 手機支付服務，但一直未有落實推行的時間，<br />\n而首部支援 LG Pay 的手機並不是旗艦級的 G7 而是中階的 K10(2018)。這部 K10(2018) 預計會配備 5.3吋 1080p解像度屏幕、Qualcomm 處理器、3GB RAM 及 32GB 記憶容量，1300萬像主鏡頭及500萬像自拍鏡頭，電池容量為 3000mAh。預計在明年1月舉行的 CES 2018 中展出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2017/12/19/%E4%BD%A0-pay-%E6%88%91%E9%83%BD-pay-lg-%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-lg-pay-2018-%E5%B9%B4%E7%99%BB%E5%A0%B4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2F2017%2F12%2F19%2F%25E4%25BD%25A0-pay-%25E6%2588%2591%25E9%2583%25BD-pay-lg-%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%2594%25AF%25E4%25BB%2598%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1-lg-pay-2018-%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%2599%25BB%25E5%25A0%25B4%2F&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=ffe275b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2017/12/19/%E4%BD%A0-pay-%E6%88%91%E9%83%BD-pay-lg-%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-lg-pay-2018-%E5%B9%B4%E7%99%BB%E5%A0%B4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLG都玩埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6673f6800a83820dd1a8f9ecd11d72cd1dd41fe8","tid":508573,"uid":164092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:35:56.000Z","msg":"香港可能2020都未有"},{"pid":"2687d75ca5f5ff2902964a13841aa622debad644","tid":508573,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:37:19.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩"},{"pid":"2e702f5c450abfe6ba12a6c1d12970b206685c8d","tid":508573,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:26:33.000Z","msg":"Samsung pay 唔係都可以當磁卡用咩？"},{"pid":"1ff80a227c71e78f7efd1e3455948ea8c0f19e91","tid":508573,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:31:50.000Z","msg":"依家啲機都開始轉晒做讀晶片啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8274a02a3449508e9d829d1b74c8d40223c72fb5","tid":508573,"uid":92477,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:51:44.000Z","msg":"lg呢類三線品牌<br />\n全球市佔4%都唔知有冇<br />\n學乜三星apple<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53a6b46febcac411fbf1b3ae69c8acf935e9ac3","tid":508573,"uid":33077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e702f5c450abfe6ba12a6c1d12970b206685c8d","tid":508573,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T12:26:33.000Z","msg":"Samsung pay 唔係都可以當磁卡用咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T13:11:35.000Z","msg":"三星個個好似專利左 佢應該係近似個類技術"},{"pid":"559e3b6b87942bc0ffad65b137e3750803645282","tid":508573,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T14:21:57.000Z","msg":"WMC 同 NFC 應該差唔多？"},{"pid":"c8c830860fa0075578ea8c1a07d199b8a63267bb","tid":508573,"uid":164092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"559e3b6b87942bc0ffad65b137e3750803645282","tid":508573,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T14:21:57.000Z","msg":"WMC 同 NFC 應該差唔多？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T11:21:12.000Z","msg":"差好遠 WMC 係同 MST 差唔多 NFC 唔可以用傳統卡機畀錢"}]}